Class ActiveExam

  • java.lang.Object
    • resources.ActiveExam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ActiveExam
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The class that contains the data of exam that has been activated. This is the class that represents the exam with it's own execution code.
